equency limiting case\nthe phase velocity and the attenuation coefficient are determined for forced\nwaves. In the small wavenumber limiting case it is shown that there exist four\nlongitudinal eigenmodes, two of them corresponding to propagating sound modes\nand two associated with non-propagating diffusive modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2013 10:29:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-16"}
